    "description": "Pocket Rocket is designed with speed-running in mind, our design philosophy was speed first, questions later.<br>The questions being classics such as: &quot;Why is this so hard!?&quot; and &quot;Oh come on I almost had it this time, right?&quot;<br><br>It's a game about maneuvering a small space rocket through obstacles to get the fastest possible scores.<br>After you've beaten levels, you can retry them racing your own past ghost to improve your skills and your score!<br>The game features obstacles like, but not limited to:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Boosters<br></li><li>Gravity Fields<br></li><li>Rotating Obstacles</li></ul><br>All of these placed carefully to make you really feel the challenge and endure the pain.<br>Try over and over again to beat a level only to watch that one guy (you know who) beat it in one go.<br><br>So come on down to Pocket Rocket town and have yourself a wonderful time amongst the stars!",
